Created by Justice Stiles
This software is offered as-is with no warranties or gaurentees of suitability 
for any purpose.

To compile the interface:

addJob.c displayAll.c flushBuff.c getJob.c load.c main.c menu.c reminder.h
removeJob.c safer_gets.c save.c searchJobs.c


To compile the daemon:

addJob.c deleteJob.c dmain.c executeJob.c freeList.c load.c reminder.h 
save.c 

To use the system:

Run the daemon as a background process.  Invoke the reminder interface to add and
remove jobs from the system.  The system requires a properly installed and 
configured command line email client to work and will send messages through the 
mail address configured in the mail client.


